<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天因为收到了圣诞老人的礼物，<delay8 />
实在太开心了，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />于是睡觉的时候梦见了圣诞老人！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这都是多亏了你<delay20 />
平安把礼物送到我手上啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你啦！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为昨天<delay20 />收到了
圣诞老人的礼物，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我今天也还是很兴奋哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />借着这股劲，<delay20 />
明年我也要获得礼物！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
谢谢你送来圣诞礼物！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我超开心的哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为这个，<delay8 />你变成了圣诞老人，<delay20 />
出现在我梦里啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天的圣诞礼物，<delay20 />
谢谢你啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我实在太高兴了，<delay20 />醒过来的时候
才发现竟然抱着礼物睡着了！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么明年也拜托你啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />昨天收到了<tag a="110" b="3" /><delay8 />
和圣诞老人的双重礼物，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是超级棒的一天啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圣诞老人给的礼物当然很叫人高兴，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但还是<delay8 />来自对手的礼物<delay20 />
能让人感受到成倍的快乐呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天的礼物，谢谢啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能收到你和圣诞老人的
双重礼物，<delay20 />我很开心哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你果然是我最棒的对手，<delay20 />
同时也是我最好的朋友！<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />期待你明年的礼物哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今天是圣诞节，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有没有<delay8 />什么计划啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔，<delay8 />不管是不是圣诞节，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的锻炼计划
都排得满满当当啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">昨天不是平安夜吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想着<delay8 />要是能见到圣诞老人就好了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />于是晚上一直在努力熬夜。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />醒过来才发现原来还是睡着了，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果今年也没能见到圣诞老人啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>